headline: Commonwealth LNG Signs Agreement to Provide LNG to EQT
summary: The agreement provides for the sale of 1 million metric tons per annum of LNG for 20 years from Commonwealth's 9.5 mtpa export facility.

headline: EQT Inks 20-Year LNG Purchase Agreement to Diversify Its Portfolio
summary: EQT secures a 20-year LNG supply deal with Commonwealth LNG, expanding its export portfolio and boosting global market reach.
